        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Affirmations for Day 10 of the sleep arc. Calm is not a destination to arrive at. It is what remains when the noise stops. These affirmations work with the identity shift from 'someone who struggles to sleep' to 'someone who sleeps'.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to affirmation practice? Read ",
